topLevelComment.author: GoCode Media
topLevelComment.text: Quincy Larson, a great man helping the World though Coding. I really appreciate the opportunity you are giving people like us. I must say that I actually first got iintroduced to the world  of web through FCC. Thanks a million. And just to pay back and as well to stay motivated, I have  started my YouTube channel called GoCode Media to stay motivated at learning web development.  I will appreciate your feedback and support on my channel. Please check out my channel and remember to subscribe. Thanks
